data.description: Immaculately clean and maintained home in Burson Ranch near Pahrump. Original owners, home is smoke, pet free and has whole home top of the line water filtration and softener. Home features vinyl plank flooring throughout the home. The kitchen has granite countertops, an island with breakfast bar, built-in microwave, and stove.  Ceiling fans in the great room and bedrooms.  Master bedroom connects to the bathroom with a garden tub, separate glass shower, double sink vanity and separate toilet area. The bathroom connects to a large walk-in closet. The second bedroom also has a walkin closet. SimpliSafe security system installed. Landscaped front and back yard. Covered concrete patio with pull down sun shades. All windows have removable sunscreens. Walled in community. Only $40 per month HOA.
